OL,3,CMan jailed for setting fire to major
OL,4,Cevents venue
OL,6,FA man who set fire to the Bournemouth
OL,7,FInternational Centre has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor two years and two months.
OL,10,FShane Wilson, 38, of no fixed abode,
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to arson following the
OL,12,Ffire in August last year.
OL,14,FWilson, who was homeless at the time,
OL,15,Fwas charged with arson with
OL,16,Frecklessness which could have
OL,17,Fendangered life.
