OL,6,FThe court heard that #53,000 worth of
OL,7,Fdamage was caused even though the fire
OL,8,Fwas quickly brought under control by
OL,9,Ffirefighters.
OL,11,FWilson had 58 convictions for 120
OL,12,Foffences - mainly violence, dishonesty
OL,13,Fand criminal damage, and history of
OL,14,Falcohol and drug use.
OL,16,FThe Judge said previous drug
OL,17,Frehabilitation efforts had not worked.
OL,18,FWilson was arrested at the scene,
OL,19,Fclaiming he "heard voices that said he
OL,20,Fshould do it."
