OL,3,CMan jailed for setting fire to major
OL,4,Cevents venue
OL,6,FIan Jeffries, Senior Crown Prosecutor,
OL,7,Fof the Crown Prosecution Service,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This reckless act posed a clear
OL,9,Fdanger to life.
OL,11,F"After setting fire to wicker chairs
OL,12,Finside the Bournemouth International
OL,13,FCentre, Shane Wilson made no effort to
OL,14,Fextinguish the flames or call for
OL,15,Fhelp, instead leaving the fire to
OL,16,Fspread unchecked.
OL,18,F"His actions risked the lives of
OL,19,Fanyone nearby and those whose
OL,20,Fprofessional duty required them to
OL,21,Frespond.
