OL,3,CMan jailed for setting fire to major
OL,4,Cevents venue
OL,6,F"He could not have known whether staff
OL,7,Fwere still inside, and the
OL,8,Fconsequences could have been
OL,9,Fcatastrophic.
OL,11,F"The Crown Prosecution Service worked
OL,12,Fwith Dorset Police to build a strong
OL,13,Fcase, resulting in Wilson pleading
OL,14,Fguilty.
OL,16,F"We hope that today's sentence makes
OL,17,Fclear that perpetrators of such
OL,18,Fdangerous and irresponsible behaviour
OL,19,Fwill be brought to justice."
